# Linteum Verba - Rich Text Editor

A feature-rich text editor built with Tkinter and TTK Bootstrap using the Canvas widget.

## Features

- Line numbers
- Code folding
- Syntax highlighting
- Text selection and editing
- Modern UI with TTK Bootstrap

## Requirements

- Python 3.7+
- ttkbootstrap>=1.10.1
- pygments>=2.15.0

## Installation

1. Clone this repository
2. Install the required packages:
   ```
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

## Usage

Run the main application:
```
python Source/Python/main.py
```
